title: Millie & Keisha Jackson Pt. 1
itunes:title: Millie & Keisha Jackson Pt. 1
description:
Singer Millie Jackson is joined by her daughter and fellow songstress Keisha Jackson for an Atlanta taping of Questlove Supreme. In Part One, Millie Jackson speaks about writing and producing provocative and popular songs that were decades ahead of their time. Millie recalls checking Aretha Franklin, performing her Grammy-nominated hit, and making a profound song that confused and upset Gospel audiences. She sings too. Just like Millie Jackson, this QLS is bold, raw, and honest.
